---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main style="
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    min-height: 80vh;
  ">

    <!-- 页面标题 -->
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <h1 style="
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4f46e5, #d946ef);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        color: transparent;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      ">
        关于我
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666;">
        了解更多我的经历、技能与想法
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 个人简介卡片 -->
    <div style="
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    ">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #1f2937;">
        👨‍💻 我是谁？
      </h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        你好，我是 <strong>YETIANs</strong>，一名热爱前端开发与视觉设计的开发者。
        我喜欢用代码创造干净、现代、有温度的界面，让技术与美学完美结合。
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #4b5563;">
        从最初写简单的 HTML/CSS，到现在使用 Astro、JavaScript 等现代框架构建完整项目，
        我始终保持学习热情，不断探索更好的用户体验与交互方式。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 技能栈 -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #1f2937;">
        🛠️ 我的技能栈
      </h2>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem;">
        <div style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 12px;">
          <h3 style="font-weight: 600; color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">前端开发</h3>
          <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 0.95rem;">HTML / CSS / JavaScript / Astro / React</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 12px;">
          <h3 style="font-weight: 600; color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">设计与工具</h3>
          <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 0.95rem;">Figma / Photoshop / Git / VS Code</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 12px;">
          <h3 style="font-weight: 600; color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">其他能力</h3>
          <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 0.95rem;">响应式开发 / 性能优化 / 交互设计</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 联系方式 -->
    <div style="
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    ">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        📬 联系我
      </h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; opacity: 0.9;">
        如果你对我的作品感兴趣，或者想一起合作，欢迎随时联系我！
      </p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="mailto:yejun6252@gmail.com" style="
          padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
          background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
          color: white;
          border-radius: 10px;
          text-decoration: none;
          font-weight: 500;
          transition: background 0.3s;
        ">
          📧 发送邮件
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/YETIANs" target="_blank" style="
          padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
          background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
          color: white;
          border-radius: 10px;
          text-decoration: none;
          font-weight: 500;
          transition: background 0.3s;
        ">
          🐱 GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>
</Layout>